{"tid":2422240,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"泰國總理巴育最後關頭放棄打科興疫苗 轉而打英國阿斯利康疫苗","createTime":"2021-02-25T05:06:45.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-25T07:37:26.000Z","uid":28114,"like":49,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"49dbf33f4540e357bc79bb2d5188252e6cc867d8","tid":2422240,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T05:06:45.000Z","msg":"疫苗抵達 捨棄中國疫苗 泰國總理自願接種英國疫苗<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://visionthai.net/article/prayut-get-astrazeneca-shot/?\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvisionthai.net%2Farticle%2Fprayut-get-astrazeneca-shot%2F%3F&d=L6ZqOc%2BI4Gry4yTyS7cXFT632Ab34%2FJQlYP9Mjrnz38%3D&h=85d1d150\" target=\"_blank\">https://visionthai.net/article/prayut-get-astrazeneca-shot/?</a><br />\n<br />\n泰國政府向中國科興(Sinovac Biotech)公司採購的新冠肺炎(COVID-19)疫苗首批今天(24日)抵泰。泰國總理巴育(Prayut Chan-o-cha)表示，他願意率先接種疫苗，但尷尬的是，有醫生警告，科興疫苗只在18歲至59歲間的受試者測試，疫苗對今年67歲的巴育有沒有效，以及會不會產生副作用都不得而知，但隨後官員澄清，巴育將接種的是適用所有年齡層的英國阿斯利康(AstraZeneca)的疫苗。<br />\n衛生部長：國家領袖第一個接種疫苗很重要<br />\n<br />\n根據《鮮新聞》、《曼谷郵報》報導，副總理兼衛生部長阿努廷(Anutin Charnvirakul)為了讓民眾對疫苗有信心，打算讓泰國總理挽起袖子，成為第一個接種疫苗的國人。但卻被醫生打臉，巴育的年紀67歲，已經超出適合施打科興疫苗的18歲至59歲範圍。<br />\n<br />\n阿努廷昨天(23日)澄清，今天中國科興和英國阿斯利康的疫苗都會抵達泰國，科興疫苗的數量約有20萬劑，阿斯利康的疫苗則有11.7萬劑，巴育將接種的是英國製藥公司阿斯利康的疫苗，「巴育將軍作為國家的領導人，第一個接種新冠肺炎疫苗是件重要事」。阿斯利康的疫苗適用不同年齡的民眾。<br />\n<br />\n阿努廷並提到，兩種新冠肺炎疫苗都需要施打兩劑，科興疫苗兩劑要間隔14天至28天，阿斯利康則要間隔6週。民眾一開始需親自至醫療機構接種疫苗，並在接種後靜待半小時，觀察是否有不適症狀。<br />\n<br />\n剩餘120萬劑科興疫苗將在接下來兩個月陸續抵泰<br />\n<br />\n巴育昨主持疫情指揮中心會議後接受媒體採訪表示，20萬劑疫苗今日抵泰後，政府約需要2到3天時間準備施打疫苗事宜，一切就緒之後，他準備率先接種疫苗。<br />\n<br />\n泰國公共衛生部與中國的科興生物技術公司簽訂採購協議，採購200萬劑新冠肺炎疫苗，首批20萬劑今天將由泰航專機從北京載運至泰國，預計3月底前再交付80萬劑，4月底前交付100萬劑。"},{"pid":"ff9a3e358656d26b8dcfbc2a2ea2b68a3dcba2d3","tid":2422240,"uid":2419,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T05:07:32.000Z","msg":"犯國安法 拉得"},{"pid":"878c6432f5ffc0a7a81ef4638bb6ec80f642fcb1","tid":2422240,"uid":28114,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T05:07:44.000Z","msg":"身體很誠實<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7b0fdc9c10b818f0f4d12d272e2736c61c26b60","tid":2422240,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T05:08:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6006bc70002c2bc64023b24e48a407b8a052a026","tid":2422240,"uid":41116,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T05:08:37.000Z","msg":"泰國行省領導人都唔打"},{"pid":"8e7042eafb5e3beec122513af88a301d0e0cc0cb","tid":2422240,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T05:08:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cf9575eeb44cedeeec63ed737cdfb3d742d494a","tid":2422240,"uid":79563,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"878c6432f5ffc0a7a81ef4638bb6ec80f642fcb1","tid":2422240,"uid":28114,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T05:07:44.000Z","msg":"身體很誠實<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T05:09:08.000Z","msg":"自己條命仔<br />\n<br />\n當然係選最好<br />\n<br />\n賤民就打科興<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecd247229100b85d59fdafa9803e4df481d58e13","tid":2422240,"uid":51271,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T05:09:34.000Z","msg":"口裡說好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"